snippet.title: The Empowered Empath
snippet.description:
Practical advice, survival and 'Thrival'' tips for Empaths and sensitives. Come join a community of fellow Empaths consciously choosing to actualize their gifts and deepen their Spirituality in a meaningful way. My mission is to create a haven for Empaths and energy sensitives to empower each other, take response-ability and transmute energies like a boss! Videos are posted weekly every Thursday and community engagement is encouraged!
So many are awakening now in the new energies we are experiencing. The Empowered Empath is meant to a space for fellow sensitives and empaths to come together and support one another in this spiritual journey.
